# Web3Forms access key for the contact form.
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com and enter info@global1media.com as the destination.
# 2. Web3Forms emails an access key to that inbox.
# 3. Copy the key here, then copy this file to `.env` (or `.env.local`).
# All contact-form submissions are delivered to the inbox tied to this key.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
